[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "ふー、体を動かしたら少しすっきりした！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00276",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "わんぱくな王女様っすね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00277",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でもクレオはなんで軍に入ったの？\nランターナには天命の規則もないよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00278",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん。私には兄が二人いてね、オルペウス兄さんは\n内政ができて、リヒャルト兄さんは、まぁ、器用",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00279",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それで私は何ができるかっていうと……\n武芸については、高い評価をもらってたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00280",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "昔からお城の中で過ごすより\n抜け出して外を走り回るのが好きだったのだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00281",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "はー、なるほど、鏑矢さんと似たような感じ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00282",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "それにみんなの面倒を見るのも好きだし、\n部下たちと過ごすのも好きなんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00283",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "同じ部隊の仲間は戦友であり、\n家族のようなものでもありますもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00284",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん、だから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00285",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "白夜の騎士ユナとかあなたみたいな\n強くて素敵な淑女になりたくて努力してるの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00286",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "頑張って筋肉をつけたんだよ！\nほら、王女の筋肉を見たまえよ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00287",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "わ、ほんとだ！　めっちゃ筋肉ついてる！\nこれが、あの強さの秘訣なんすね……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00288",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私の筋肉も見事だと、ほめている、称えている。\nヒューッて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00289",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "二人とも、立派な筋肉ですこと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00290",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "随分、奥まで来たわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00291",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "求める素材まではもう少し！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00292",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "でも、奥地ほど強力な魔物がいるのが\n世の常だから。気を付けていきましょうね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00293",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "待って。奥から音がする。\n金属音、これは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00294",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ええ、武器……しかも長物の音。\n誰かが魔物の群れと戦っているみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00295",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……ほんとだ、そう言われてみると\n戦っている音が聞こえてくる、かも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00296",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "助けてあげなくちゃ！\n急ごう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00297",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "フッ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00298",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "見つけた！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00299",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "なんて速い攻撃……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00300",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "必要ないかもだけど、相手は数も多いし！\nそこの素敵なお姉さん、助けさせて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00301",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "ありがとう！　じゃあ、お姉さん、\nお言葉に甘えちゃおっかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00302",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "来るっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00303",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]